<h3><span class="marker">How does it work?</span></h3>

<p>When your public key is added to a public keyserver open the link: </p>

<p><span class="marker">encrypt.to/{your-email}</span> or <span class="marker">encrypt.to/{your-key-id}</span></p>

<p>For example: <a href="/0x5f43f53fb41d959a">encrypt.to/0x5f43f53fb41d959a</a> belongs to <a href="http://pgpkey.org/pks/lookup?op=vindex&search=0x5f43f53fb41d959a&fingerprint=on"> this email</a>.</p>

<p>If not, upload your public key to a <a href="http://pgpkey.org/">public keyserver</a>.</p>

